WEBVTT

NOTE Skit begins at anchor #4.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
<v Announcer (Eric Idle)>
And now for something completely the same - a man with three buttocks. [action] Phone rings; answers. 'Hullo? …Oh, did we.' [action] Puts phone down. And now for something completely different. A man with three noses.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.000
<v Off-screen Voice (John Cleese)>
He's not here yet!

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.000
<v Announcer (Eric Idle)>
Two noses?

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:16.000
[action] Women's Institute audience applauds. A man flourishes handkerchief, blows nose; then hides hanky in shirt and blows again from the elbow. Audience applauds again.

